<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<a href="./RavenRed">RavenRed</a>: Just a few ideas for some Uber-Tomes with Multiple School Spells: 
    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 Mighty Tome of the Elements (Fire, Earth, Water, Air) 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Mighty Tome of the Ethereal (Mana, Meta, Temporal, Conveyance) 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Mighty Tome of the Living (Mind, Nature, Divination) 
</p>
</li>

    </ul>


<p>
These mighty Tomes should be 30-40lbs each, ridiculously rare and -10% mana (explanation for that? uh... um... they're so powerful they suck up the magic of the bearer... yeah, that'll fly) 
</p>
<p>
Convenience is a wonderful thing, but you will have to pay for it.  
</p>
